{*
<p>Miranda NG is a successor of a popular multi-protocol instant messaging client for Windows - Miranda IM. Very light on system resources and extremely fast.</p>

<hr/>
<h3>Protocol Support{* ({= count($protocols)})* }</h3>
<ul n:inner-foreach="$protocols as $protocol" class="threecols">
<li>{$protocol}</li>
</ul>

<h3>Supported Operating Systems</h3>
<ul>
<li>Windows 2003 / XP / Vista / 7 / 8</li>
</ul>

<h3>Miranda NG is designed, written & supported by:</h3>

<ul n:inner-foreach="$team as $user => $role" class="twocols">
	<li>{$user} <span class="aka">aka</span> {$role[0]}</li>
</ul>
*}
